headline: Assessing Trane Technologies After Its Strong Multi Year Rally and Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Wondering if Trane Technologies at around $411 a share is still worth your money, or if the big gains are already behind it? This article walks through what the numbers actually say about its value. The stock has pulled back about 2% over the last week and 7.9% over the last month, but it is still up 10% year to date and 142.3% over 3 years and 210.6% over 5 years.
